data_tam_commits <- read.table(file = "tam_trat.csv", sep = "\t", header = T)
data_tam_commits_arch <- data_tam_commits[1:232,]
data_tam_commits_narch <- data_tam_commits[233:464,]
pca_tam <- prcomp(data_tam_commits, scale. = T)
pca_tam_arch <- prcomp(data_tam_commits_arch, scale. = T)
pca_tam_narch <- prcomp(data_tam_commits_narch, scale. = T)
View(pca_tam$rotation)
View(pca_tam_arch$rotation)
View(pca_tam_narch$rotation)
